    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for reliable transportation. Mechanically, the car is sound and has been regularly maintained, though it does show its age through several cosmetic imperfections. The exterior features some noticeable scratches and minor dings consistent with its mileage, and the interior exhibits typical wear on the upholstery and dashboard. All major systems are functional, but a buyer should expect the aesthetic character of a well-used vehicle. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that still has plenty of life left in it.",
