      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional specimen of automotive excellence, this vehicle is offered in impeccable, showroom-grade condition. Every facet of this motorcar\u2014from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior\u2014reflects a standard of care that borders on the obsessive. Meticulously maintained and mechanically beyond reproach, this unit represents a premier opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
