      "description": "Presented in impeccable, showroom-grade condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every aspect, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of care that is rarely encountered in the secondary market. Meticulously maintained and mechanically absolute, this offering provides a distinguished driving experience for the most discerning enthusiast.",
